    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Category</strong>: Clan <br /><strong>Prerequisite</strong>: Kamizuru Clan, Level 4+ <br />Your hive instinctivey swarms to your defense at the first sign of danger causing your foes to hesitate to attack. You gain the following benifits;</p><ul><li><p>Increase your Wisdom or Intelligen</p></li><li><p>You may add your Wisdom modifier in place of Dexterity to your Initiative bonus.</p></li><li>When a hostile creature that can see you first rolls initiative, they suffer a penalty to their initiative roll equal to half your prof. bonus (rounded down).</li><li>You can't be surprised while conscious.ce score by 1, to a maximum of 20.</li></ul>",
